---
title: Mozzarella & Roasted Red Pepper Sandos with an Almond-Studded Green Salad
description: What could be better than a caprese salad, you ask? A caprese sandwich! We layered pesto,  tomatoes, mixed greens, and fresh mozz into ciabatta. To complete the lunch, we added a crisp salad with crunchy almonds. You can meal prep the sandwich in the morning, and whether you’re headed to work or staying in, you’ll be stoked come lunchtime.
